    <div class="wrapper"> 
     <h1 class="main-header">WeConnect</h1> 
     <p class="sub-header">Optimists are easy to recognize. They’re the ones taking charge, springing into action, and making a difference. Explore all the ways that these dreamers and doers from all walks of life and every discipline are creating positive change in their communities and around the world.</p> 
